   <para>When you start &app;, the following window is displayed:</para>
   <figure>
   <title>&app; main window</title>
     <screenshot><mediaobject> 
	    <imageobject><imagedata fileref="figures/trans1.2.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
	    <textobject><phrase>Screenshot  &app; main window.</phrase></textobject>

     </mediaobject></screenshot>
   </figure>

   <para>
   The &app; main window contains the following elements:
   <variablelist>
       <varlistentry><term>Menubar</term>
             <listitem>
